SUMMARY:Organizing for People of Faith Cohort
DESCRIPTION:Do you long to create change in the world? Do you wonder how to work with other people to build a world that is in alignment with the beloved community of God? \nIn this 6-session cohort\, we will identify what pressing issues you see in your community\, who has the power to improve those issues\, and how those people with that power can be moved. Taught by rev. abby mohaupt\, PhD\, an ordained minister in the Presbyterian Church (USA) with over ten years of experience in community organizing and research in social movements of the church. [Sliding Scale available.] \nSession dates and times: \nWe’ll meet via zoom on the following Tuesdays from 2:30-4pm CT: \n\nMarch 3\nMarch 10\nMarch 24\nApril 14\nApril 21\nMay 5
